name: Beatrice Bee- Print from original mixed media collage -(8X10)
description:
Whimsical mixed media collage painting of a sweet bee ready to enter Springtime with style.Beatrice Bee is quite the honey and will surely love to buzz around your home. Collage was collaged using quality papers and hand painted/drawn with charm for any quirky fun loving collector! 

This is a 8"x10" beautiful reproduction print of my original collage painting. It is printed on high quality 8" x 10" luster photo paper.

Ready for matting and framing.
*Note* Watermark will not appear in your print!
Thank you!!!!
